{"tid":2188791,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇整 西西里汁 既簡單方法","createTime":"2020-09-04T12:41:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T13:34:38.000Z","uid":232237,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"29f1b72a5d6be7f04bdc2571ff908f95fe3a9dce","tid":2188791,"uid":232237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T12:41:44.000Z","msg":"上網睇 要咁多料<br />\n西西里湯底材料：橄欖油 8毫升、洋葱碎 100克、蒜茸 15克、茄膏 30克、白酒 50毫升、碎茄肉 524克、罐頭銀魚柳 (Anchovy Fillet) 48克（連油切碎）、茄汁 138克、白醋 10毫升、中東米 (couscous) 40克、糖 39克、凍開水 900毫升、菜湯 80毫升、阿里根奴香草 1/2茶匙、雞粉 10克<br />\n<br />\n要咁樣整<br />\n<br />\n1.先煮西西里湯底，將碎茄肉、茄汁、凍開水、白醋、菜湯、糖、中東米、阿里根奴香草、罐頭銀魚柳及雞粉放入大碗拌勻。<br />\n<br />\n2.開中火燒熱鍋下橄欖油、蒜茸、洋葱碎及茄膏爆香 1分鐘，注入白酒煮 10秒，再倒入（ 1）煮 5分鐘至滾起後成西西里湯底，然後盛起<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好好食但又唔洗咁 其實有冇其他方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54ef66aaf5b2ec995cf39d41b89f3dbd69b6b4a9","tid":2188791,"uid":340796,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T13:13:39.000Z","msg":"好多都係屋企廚房必有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n主要係茄膏白酒碎茄肉Anchovy<br />\n菜湯轉水都得"},{"pid":"81443dd96153270657c30d89b59c403ac4766124","tid":2188791,"uid":373442,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T15:18:24.000Z","msg":"你個食譜邊度睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n碎茄肉 524克<br />\n罐頭銀魚柳 (Anchovy Fillet) 48克<br />\n茄汁 138克<br />\n糖 39克<br />\n<br />\n除左整甜品，我都係第一次見啲份量既尾數咁搞笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d5b14f7e65a5e871b4c5685d9db1d7dfc81e4c4","tid":2188791,"uid":232237,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"81443dd96153270657c30d89b59c403ac4766124","tid":2188791,"uid":373442,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T15:18:24.000Z","msg":"你個食譜邊度睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n碎茄肉 524克<br />\n罐頭銀魚柳 (Anchovy Fillet) 48克<br />\n茄汁 138克<br />\n糖 39克<br />\n<br />\n除左整甜品，我都係第一次見啲份量既尾數咁搞笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T17:04:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.xuite.net/blog/windyleaf99/hkblog/113198872\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.xuite.net%2Fblog%2Fwindyleaf99%2Fhkblog%2F113198872&d=HMiOmB7b1AqxO%2BCwCPl1caix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=6d9929b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.xuite.net/blog/windyleaf99/hkblog/113198872</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b78d536bb48d4625bd792fe5e9c0904b3a06e74a","tid":2188791,"uid":192409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T17:05:26.000Z","msg":"西汁就有方法"},{"pid":"bc66fb253b9f3ef0103877035b284dd81f92ebc3","tid":2188791,"uid":232237,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"54ef66aaf5b2ec995cf39d41b89f3dbd69b6b4a9","tid":2188791,"uid":340796,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T13:13:39.000Z","msg":"好多都係屋企廚房必有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n主要係茄膏白酒碎茄肉Anchovy<br />\n菜湯轉水都得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T17:05:34.000Z","msg":"下 菜湯轉水個味唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37ce7826ff8334b1744eea1c8